      <p>Now we can see from <xref ref-type="fig" rid="gks1450-F2">Figure 2</xref> that the sequence-order effect of a DNA sequence can be, to some extent, reflected through a set of sequence-correlation factors <inline-formula><inline-graphic xlink:href="gks1450i50.jpg"/></inline-formula>
